    public class BaseBusBranchControlImpl
extends NameTagImpl
implements BaseBusBranchControl
    An implementation of the model object 'Base Bus Branch Control'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Adjust Status
    • Adj Control Type
    • Control Mode
    • Desired Control Range
